[04:01.54]We needed no further warning. | 我们不再需要更多的警告了。
[04:04.25]Turning back down the main street, | 我们转身沿着主要街道往回走，
[04:06.60]we quickened our pace and made our way rapidly towards the stream where we hoped the boatman was waiting. | 加快了脚步，迅速朝小溪走去，我们希望船夫还在那里等着。